{"605266":{"detail":{"date":"2018-10-10","platform":"WEB","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/01/c6/605266_Iy3Gl.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/01/c6/605266_Iy3Gl.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/01/c6/605266_Iy3Gl.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/01/c6/605266_Iy3Gl.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/01/c6/605266_Iy3Gl.jpg"},"summary":"美味しいを囲むこと。\r\nそれが、オタフクソースの目指す「幸せのかたち」です。\r\n食の周りに人が集う団らんのひととき、そこには、楽しさ、優しさ、心地よさが自然に生まれます。\r\n\r\nオタフクソースの商品、そしてお好み焼は、\r\nさまざまな境界線を超えていく「BORDERLESS FOOD（ボーダレスフード）」です。\r\n\r\n人と人の心の垣根を越えて、その先にある笑顔を生み出していくために。\r\n地球規模の環境に配慮しながら、この小さな「幸せのかたち」という人々の輪が、\r\n世界中に大きく広がっていく未来に貢献していきます。","name":"小さな幸せを、地球の幸せに。","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"片渊须直","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"BORDERLESS HAPPINESS"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"3"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2018年10月10日"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"https://www.otafuku.co.jp/corporate/lp/animation/"},{"key":"导演","value":"片渕須直"},{"key":"脚本","value":"片渕須直"},{"key":"音乐","value":"コトリンゴ"},{"key":"人物原案","value":"こうの史代"},{"key":"动画制作","value":"MAPPA"},{"key":"链接","value":[{"k":"YouTube 第1集","v":"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=S5OB3EDmiNU&t=8s&pp=2AEIkAIB"},{"k":"YouTube 第2集","v":"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Eyzb0Lgf0Y4&t=11s&pp=2AELkAIB"},{"k":"YouTube 第3集","v":"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=B5q7tBxsmQQ&t=120s&pp=2AF4kAIB"}]}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":1,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"total_episodes":3,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":1,"wish":0,"collect":5,"doing":0},"id":605266,"eps":3,"meta_tags":[],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},"episodes":[{"airdate":"2018-10-10","name":"わたしの名は オオタフクコ「その1」","name_cn":"","duration":"00:01:45","desc":"","ep":1,"sort":1,"id":1589411,"subject_id":605266,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":105},{"airdate":"2018-11-08","name":"わたしの名は オオタフクコ「その2」","name_cn":"","duration":"00:01:52","desc":"","ep":2,"sort":2,"id":1589412,"subject_id":605266,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":112},{"airdate":"2019-02-06","name":"わたしの名は オオタフクコ「その3」","name_cn":"","duration":"00:02:10","desc":"","ep":3,"sort":3,"id":1589413,"subject_id":605266,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":130}],"updatedAt":"2026-05-01T18:19:52.322Z"},"605312":{"detail":{"date":"2026-03-20","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/78/b5/605312_wz0Xt.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/78/b5/605312_wz0Xt.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/78/b5/605312_wz0Xt.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/78/b5/605312_wz0Xt.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/78/b5/605312_wz0Xt.jpg"},"summary":"おしりが前にあることが特徴的なヒーロー\"おしり前マン\"。\r\n\r\nおしりが前にあるため街の平和を脅かす者を許さないおしり前マンは、日々巻き起こる様々な問題を、新たな仲間との出会いや過酷な試練を乗り越えて解決していく。\r\n\r\nそんな中、不穏な動きが…。かつて存在したと言い伝えられている\"おしり前帝国\"を復活させ、人々を支配しようとする邪悪な影が、世界を覆いつくそうとしていた。","name":"おしり前マン〜復活のおしり前帝国〜","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恶俗","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"谷口崇","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"上映年度","value":"2026年3月20日"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"https://saigate.co.jp/oshirifront/"},{"key":"Copyright","value":"©2026映画「おしり前マン」/ 谷口崇"},{"key":"导演","value":"谷口崇"},{"key":"主題歌演出","value":"「おしり前マンの歌」 谷口崇"},{"key":"原作","value":"谷口崇"},{"key":"脚本","value":"米山和仁、谷口崇"},{"key":"人物设定","value":"谷口崇"},{"key":"作画监督","value":"谷口崇"},{"key":"美术监督","value":"谷口崇"},{"key":"动画导演","value":"奇志戒聖"},{"key":"制作管理","value":"橋本雄、小山瑞生"},{"key":"音乐","value":"松野恭平"},{"key":"音响监督","value":"田中亮"},{"key":"音效","value":"和田俊也"},{"key":"录音调整","value":"光山利央"},{"key":"制作","value":"野添靖人、井上直子"},{"key":"音响制作","value":"スワラプロ"},{"key":"副制片